# NextAuth Configuration
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:4028
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-secret-key-here

# Google OAuth Configuration
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id-here
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret-here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 3. Create a new project or select an existing one
# 4. Enable the Google+ API
# 5. Go to "Credentials" and create OAuth 2.0 Client IDs
# 6. Set authorized redirect URIs to: http://localhost:4028/api/auth/callback/google
# 7. Copy the Client ID and Client Secret and replace the placeholders above
# 8. Replace NEXTAUTH_SECRET with a strong random string
